I see.

14:59.440 --> 14:59.840
Well, sorry.

14:59.840 --> 15:01.440
The guided missile is quite different.

15:01.440 --> 15:08.720
It's the President said it's impossible to develop a missile within a atomic or hydrogen warhead

15:08.720 --> 15:11.440
unless you're going to experiment with it.

15:11.920 --> 15:13.680
I think you must be right in that.

15:13.680 --> 15:15.680
But you wanted to talk about the peacetime uses of this.

15:15.680 --> 15:16.480
Yes, I did.

15:16.480 --> 15:19.680
I think we ought to understand this.

15:20.480 --> 15:23.920
There is no, you can, a missile is nothing but a carrier.

15:23.920 --> 15:24.320
That's right.

15:24.320 --> 15:25.840
It's like an airplane senator.

15:25.840 --> 15:27.360
It's like a railroad train.

15:27.360 --> 15:29.840
It delivers the goods to a target.

15:31.280 --> 15:32.880
Goods can be an atomic warhead.

15:32.880 --> 15:36.080
It can be an conventional TNT warhead.

15:36.080 --> 15:38.640
It could be a hydrogen warhead.

15:38.640 --> 15:39.920
It could be anything.

15:40.000 --> 15:45.120
Now the development of the missile has nothing to do with the content of the explosive in the warhead.

15:46.160 --> 15:51.040
Well, I'd understood the defense department thought that it was necessary to experiment with both of them together.

15:51.040 --> 15:53.120
But the governor may be right on it.

15:53.120 --> 15:54.320
I think that's a misunderstanding.

15:54.320 --> 15:58.480
But in any event, I would like to bring up the question of what's happening to our

15:59.600 --> 16:02.240
atomic energy commercial use program.

16:03.120 --> 16:07.840
Six years ago and three years ago, we were either had a monopoly or we were greatly in the lead.

16:08.080 --> 16:12.080
We were told in the time the atomic energy act of

16:12.880 --> 16:18.320
1954 came up that the government should not even build any demonstration

16:19.040 --> 16:21.840
reactor plants for the purpose of making electricity.

16:22.400 --> 16:24.240
That private industry would do it all.

16:24.960 --> 16:28.960
But we find now after a period of time that not one patent has been issued,

16:29.680 --> 16:34.000
there's been no private development of atomic energy for commercial purposes.

16:34.080 --> 16:35.440
No reactors have been built.

16:36.080 --> 16:42.880
Only $36 worth of electricity has been sold from a submarine prototype plant up in New York.

16:45.040 --> 16:52.800
The mean time the Soviet has been producing atomic energy from our electric power from the

16:52.800 --> 16:55.920
atomic generator since May 1954.

16:56.720 --> 16:57.760
They're building another one.

16:57.760 --> 17:01.920
They expect to have two million kilowatts and salt capacity by 60.

17:01.920 --> 17:05.760
